{
  "name": "RPlog_Battle_of_Bothawui_IV_25_ABY",
  "title": "The Iron Price at Bothawui",
  "summary": "In the orbital battle for Bothawui, a New Republic task group led by Captain Rasi Cen aboard the Mon Calamari cruiser Deliverance, with Commander Argon Brand commanding the dreadnaught Derlin, drives at the Imperial line anchored by Admiral Fields's Star Destroyer Desolator. Fields cripples the Deliverance with repeated ion barrages while the nimble Derlin rakes the Desolator's flank and engines, and the two capital ships trade devastating broadsides at close range. Both flagships are mortally wounded: the Deliverance breaks apart after delivering the planet into Republic hands, and the Desolator detonates with all hands as Fields dies on his bridge. With his admiral dead, Imperial Captain Corliss of the Annihilator negotiates terms with the now-commanding Brand, and a tense cease-fire allows an orderly Imperial withdrawal as the Republic claims Bothawui.",
